graph TD
    INPUT[Sensor Reading] --> TEMP[Classify Temp]
    INPUT --> HUMID[Classify Humidity]
    TEMP --> COMBINE[Risk Assessment]
    HUMID --> COMBINE
    COMBINE --> CHECK{Extreme?}
    CHECK -->|yes| ALERT[Issue Alert]
    CHECK -->|no| LOG[Log Normal]

